# (void) _create(value, options)

Constructs and adds a new signal.

Parameters:

  • value ( Object ) — Any value
  • options ( Object ) — The options

Options Hash: (options):

  • silent ( Boolean ) — Whether or not to trigger an event
  • before ( Signal ) — The signal after which to place it
  • after ( Signal ) — The signal before which to place it

  • options ( Object ) — The options

Options Hash: (options):

  • before ( Signal ) — The signal after which to place it
  • after ( Signal ) — The signal before which to place it

# (void) _delete(signal, options)

Deletes a signal.

Parameters:

  • signal ( Signal ) — The signal to delete
  • options ( Object ) — The options

Options Hash: (options):

  • silent ( Boolean ) — Whether or not to trigger a delete event

# (void) _remove(signal, options)

Removes a signal from the linked list. This does not delete it from the index.

Parameters:

  • signal ( Signal ) — The signal to remove
  • options ( Object ) — The options

Options Hash: (options):

  • silent ( Boolean ) — Wether or not to trigger a remove event
